com.xconns.peerdevicenet

Class NetInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xconns.peerdevicenet.NetInfo

  • public class NetInfo
extends Object
    Info of the network connecting peer devices: its type (wifi, hotspot, ...), name (SSID,...), encrypt password, interface name, support multicast or not, etc.
